你的编译器将可以处理如下的 SysY 程序:

```c
int main() {
  return 1 + 2 * -3;
}
```

## 语法规范

```ebnf
CompUnit    ::= FuncDef;

FuncDef     ::= FuncType IDENT "(" ")" Block;
FuncType    ::= "int";

Block       ::= "{" Stmt "}";
Stmt        ::= "return" Exp ";";

